HEADWORD: Tearful
<hw>Tear"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Abounding with tears;
weeping; shedding tears; <as>as, <ex>tearful</ex> eyes</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Tear"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Tear"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tearless</ent>⟦br⟧
